00:00:42.550 --> 00:00:44.990
LAURA LING: Mwanaidi Mwende
lives with her grandchildren

00:00:44.990 --> 00:00:47.010
in a small village in Tanzania.

00:00:47.010 --> 00:00:49.030
Every few days she
scours the land

00:00:49.030 --> 00:00:51.080
around her home in
search of firewood,

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:52.580
which she uses to cook.

00:00:52.580 --> 00:00:55.556
