00:02:06.530 --> 00:02:08.030
LAURA LING: As
Mwanaidi was cooking,

00:02:08.030 --> 00:02:10.250
you could hear her coughing
and her grandchildren

00:02:10.250 --> 00:02:11.780
coughing around her.

00:02:11.780 --> 00:02:14.660
And as she explained,
she has no other choice

00:02:14.660 --> 00:02:16.160
but to cook this
way even though she

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:19.770
knows that it can cause harmful
long-term health issues.

00:02:19.770 --> 00:02:23.160
What's incredible is that smoke
inhalation kills more people

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:26.340
worldwide than HIV
and malaria combined.

