I'm studying always

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:56.975
because I want to be a doctor.

00:02:56.975 --> 00:02:59.102
Sometimes I have to
walk far distance

00:02:59.102 --> 00:03:01.310
to find the place where the
electricity is available.

